item.title: The WordPress Theme for Coaches
item.dc:creator: brandid
item.content:encoded:
You became a coach to help others better their lives -- not to spend far too many hours (and dollars) frustrated with code or going back and forth with developers, only to end up with a website that doesnt live up to the credibility youve earned.
Coaching Pro is the only Genesis theme built to be highly customized to what coaches need -- with no coding knowledge necessary.

item.title: About Coaching Pro theme
item.dc:creator: brandid
item.content:encoded:
Whether you're coaching athletes or executives, you guide people to make strategic decisions that help them be their best selves. That's exactly what this theme does, too! It empowers you to showcase all you have to offer clients, and it's approachable, authoritative and appealingjust like you. With video and blog capabilities that let you speak for yourself and customizable colors and templates that suit your style, this theme is packed with features that drive traffic to your site so that the people who need your help are sure to find it. We call that a win-win.
